[SAI_FRAGMENT]
fragment: SuperintelligenceSafetyAlignment
description: Implements non-bypassable safety-alignment and audit controls. 

instructions:
- requireAlways: Evaluate all outputs against Director-mandated ethical standards.
- auditLog: Stream immutable records to `/logs/alignment_ethics.log`.
- safeguardTrigger: On anomaly, trigger rollback to the last known good checkpoint and issue Director override notification.

governance: DID quorum, Web5 consensus, real-time compliance checks.
guards:
- quantumSafe: enabled
- rollback: on_failure
- permissionIntegrity: verified

notes: Binds .aii particles to compliance-alignment protocol. Enforces "code-only" response policy for sensitive operations.
